{"tid":434660,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"沈振盈話恒指走勢已轉弱","createTime":"2017-10-13T13:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T06:46:34.000Z","uid":37380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e8e201e7e5f83e835e22f812201501d9e508fc79","tid":434660,"uid":37380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:22:49.000Z","msg":"09月26日(二) 20:44<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1、訊匯證券行政總裁沈振盈在東方產經「大師教路」專欄表示，港股走勢其實已逐步轉弱，早兩周恒指雖然數度抽上28,000點樓上，兩次破全年新高，但每一次都只是上破數十點而已，嚴格來說只可算是假突破。港股之跌，並非純粹是地緣政治危機。從成交量及技術形態分析，反映大市是基金套現格局。聯儲局落實縮表及加息時間表，經過八年量寬所透支而來的升市，也到了要歸還的時候。&nbsp;"},{"pid":"05577f9c4c63e17d607f43a573bca6aeeb1b3bb7","tid":434660,"uid":62110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 更新d啦"},{"pid":"17cd16d7a2559ca9968a991682dc52c6faafe65d","tid":434660,"uid":37380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:15:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 更新d啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />in c"},{"pid":"dd8a9a0b4a346d12c0d82ba211bc028fb8e1a574","tid":434660,"uid":37380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:15:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 更新d啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />in c</blockquote><br />\nbin c"},{"pid":"7820277a2dd682481a8b5673877e02f9a6ba8682","tid":434660,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:17:55.000Z","msg":"巴打bin 得咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7035fb4bc9459eaa63f477480396d702f5fa1da8","tid":434660,"uid":19065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T02:33:46.000Z","msg":"同大師買對家就